high_descs: Turn left, head forward, turn right, head to the stove.
Pick up the dirty pan on the back of the stove.
Turn around, bring the pan to the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink with water.
Bring the pan back to the stove on the right.
Put the pan on the stove, under the kettle.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan on the stove, under the kettle.

high_descs: turn left and walk to the kitchen counter, then turn right and walk over to the stove at the end of the room
grab the dirty sauce pan off of the stove from the back left burner
move over to the sink on your left
place the dirty sauce pan inside of the sink and rinse it off, then pick it back up
turn right and move over to the stove ahead on the right
place the clean sauce pan on the burner
anns.task_desc: place a clean sauce pan on the stove top burner

high_descs: Turn to your left then turn to your right go straight to the stove
Pick up the pan behind the kettle on the stove
Turn around and walk going to the sink
Put the pan on the sink, rinse it then pick it up
Turn to your right and head back to the stove
Place the pan under the kettle on the stove
anns.task_desc: Put the clean pan under the kettle on the stove

high_descs: Go left and then right to face the stove.
Pick the pan up from the back left of the stove.
Turn to the left and face the sink.
Put the pan in the sink, turn the water on and then off and pick the pan up.
Turn to the right and face the stove.
Put the pan down on the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan on the stove.

high_descs: turn left, walk to the stove
grab the pan on the stove
turn left, walk to the sink
put the pan in the sink, wash the pan in the sink, take the pan out
turn right, walk to the stove,
put the pan under the kettle on the stove
anns.task_desc: wash the pan in the sink, put it under the kettle on the stove

high_descs: Move to the stove to the right of the sink
Pick up a pan from the stove
Move to the sink to the left of the stove
Wash the pan in the sink with water and pick it up
Move to the stove to the right of you
Put the pan on the stove
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned pan on the stove.
